%F A394071 Equals (7/24)*(cot(Pi/7) + cot(Pi/14))*sqrt(4 - sec(Pi/14)^2) = (7/24)*(A178818 + cot(A019681))*sqrt(4 - sec(A019681)^2).
%F A394071 Equals the largest real root of 46656*x^6 - 508032*x^4 + 209916*x^2 + 2401.
